---
title: Carb Smart Cheesy Smothered Chicken with Mushroom Sauce and Mashed Potatoes
description: Is there anything better than juicy chicken thighs smothered in mushroom sauce and topped with cheddar cheese? This low carb meal has all that and more, with creamy mash and roasted carrots as the perfect sides.

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
